snippet.title: Hercules game v0.6 trailer
snippet.description:
Get the game here:
https://dimosadonis.itch.io/hercules

Hercules is a 2-D sandbox RPG in which the player experiences Greek mythology first-hand as he/she explores huge maps, caves and dungeons!
